@startuml
title Evidence Modes and Run Outcomes

left to right direction

rectangle "Configured evidence modes" as Config {
  strict_live
  cached_live
  seeded_demo
}

rectangle "Realized run outcomes" as Outcome {
  fully_live
  degraded_live
  demo_fallback
}

strict_live --> fully_live : all required live providers succeed
strict_live --> degraded_live : live run completes,\nprovider partially fails
strict_live --> "hard failure" : required evidence missing\nand seeded fallback would be needed
cached_live --> degraded_live : replayed prior live artifacts\nfor stable demo
seeded_demo --> demo_fallback : deterministic fallback

note bottom
`degraded_live` is a run outcome, not a configured evidence mode.
`cached_live` is a configured replay mode.
end note

@enduml
